# Checkouts must be byte-identical on every platform: the bundled model
# resources are hash-pinned in the catalog and validated at load time, so a
# CRLF-converting checkout (e.g. Windows CI's autocrlf) would break both the
# pin tests and the packaged application.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png -text
*.icns -text
*.ico -text
*.gz -text
*.bin -text
